description: Kelly & Sophie are recording from Kelly's house today in the middle of moving day! Kelly tells more stories about her trip home to Atlanta, their visit to Athens and does a deep dive into the problems within youth sports.The Morning After podcast is produced by ACTIONPARK MEDIA.Follow us on Social Media:@actionparkmediagroup@themorningafter.kellystafford
